WEBVTT

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:31.496
for 15 years,

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:33.535
with every film, with every lawsuit,

00:08:33.559 --> 00:08:34.856
with every campaign,

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:37.216
I thought we were making the nation safer

00:08:37.240 --> 00:08:38.640
for the next generation.

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:43.840
And then my son was born.

00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:55.000
In a time ...

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:58.856
when hate crimes against our communities

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:01.520
are at the highest
they have been since 9/11.